quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  49,1,"Yaa yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnde! Ra rengd-y Wẽnd ne A Tẽn-tʋʋmã taoor ye, la y zoe Wẽnde, ad Wẽnd yɑɑ Wʋmdɑ n yaa Mita."
  49,2,"Yaa yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnde! Ra zẽk-y y koeesã Nabiyaamã koεεg zug ye, la y ra porg-a ne gomd wala yãmb ne taab porbã ye, tɩ y tʋʋm na n wa lʋɩ tɩ y pa miẽ ye."
  49,3,"Ad neb nins sẽn sikd b koeesã Wẽnd Tẽn-tʋʋmã nengẽ wã, bãmb la neb nins Wẽnd sẽn yɩlg-b rãmb sũy ne wẽn-zoεεga, bãmb rãmb tara yaafg la keoor sẽn zɩse."
  49,4,"Ad neb nins sẽn boond-b foom rotã poayẽ wã, b wʋsgã fãa pa tar yam ye."
  49,5,"Bãmb sã n da maanẽ sugri hal tɩ fo wa yi n kẽng b nengẽ, rẽ n yɩɩdẽ sõmblem ne bãmba; la Wẽnd yaa Yaafd n yaa Yoalsda."
  49,6,"Yaa yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnde! Dĩin yit sã n wa yãmb nengẽ ne kɩbare, bɩ y bao vẽenem, la y ra rʋʋg neb ne zɩɩlem tɩ yãmb lebg n maan mims ne yãmb sẽn tʋm bũmb ningã ye."
  49,7,"La y bãng tɩ Wẽnd Tẽn-tʋʋm bee yãmb pʋgẽ; a sã n da tũudẽ yãmb yεl wʋsg fãa pʋgẽ, rag n na pak yãmba. La Wẽnde maana limaoongã nonglemã yãmb nengẽ, la A faas-a yãmb sũyẽ wã, la A kisg kɩfend yãmb nengẽ, la Dĩin yiibu, la Wẽnd kɩɩsgo, bãmb rãmbã la kãndgdba."
  49,8,"Yaa yɩɩdlem sẽn yi Wẽnd nengẽ la neema, la Wẽnd yaa Mita, n yaa bʋʋd Mita."
  49,9,"La sull a yiib sẽn yi Muumin-rãmbẽ wã sã n wa zabd taaba, bɩ y maneg b yiibã sʋka, la b yiibã a yembr sã n maan n zʋʋg a to wã zugu, bɩ y zab ne sẽn maan n zʋʋg-a wã hal t'a wa lebg n tʋg Wẽnd bʋʋdẽ wã. A sã n lebge, bɩ y maneg b yiibã sʋka ne sɩda, la y tẽeg tɩrga, ad Wẽnd nonga tẽeg tɩrg rãmba."
  49,10,"Ad Muumin-rãmbã yaa ma-biisi, bɩ y maneg-y ma-biirã ne taab sʋka, la y zoe Wẽnde, ti sãnd-sãnde, b na yols-yã."
  49,11,"Yaa yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnde! Neb ra yaal neba, tɩ b tõe n wa yɩɩ sõma n yɩɩd bãmba. Pagb me ra yaal pagba, tɩ b tõe n wa yɩɩ sõma n yɩɩd bãmba. Ra y rɑ zɑng y tɑɑb ye, ra pʋd-y taab sond-wẽns ye. Dĩin yiib yʋʋr yɩ wẽng liimaoong poorẽ, la ned ning sẽn pa tuub-a…Bãmb rãmb la wẽgdba."
  49,12,"Yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnde! Zãag-y tẽ-wẽnsã wʋsgo; ad tẽebã sãnda yaa zunuubu. La y ra pẽes ye, yãmb sãnda ra wɩd sãnda ye. Rẽ yĩnga yãmb ned kam fãa nongame n na n wãb a ma-bi-taag nemd t'a sã n ki? Rẽnd yãmb kisa rẽ. La y zoe Wẽnde, ad Wẽnd yaa tuubg rɛɛgda, n yaa yolsg naaba."
  49,13,"Yaa yãmb a neba! Ad Tõnd naana yãmb tɩ y yaa roap la pagba; n maan yãmb tɩ y yaa zãma la buud-buudu, tɩ y na bãng taab yĩnga. Ad yãmb sẽn yɩɩd-a ne waoor Wẽnd nengẽ yaa sẽn yɩɩd-a ne wẽn-zoεεga. Ad Wẽnd yaa mita, n yaa minim tẽng-n-biiga."
  49,14,"Weoogẽ laarb-rãmb yeelame: ""tõnd kõo sɩda"". Yeele: ""yamb pa kõ sɩd ye, la yeel-y yã: ''tõnd sak n tũume'', bala liimaoong nan pa kẽ yãmb sũyẽ wã nand ye. La yãmb sã n tũ Wẽnd ne A Tẽn-tʋʋmã, A pa boogd yãmb y tʋʋmẽ wã ba fʋɩ ye, ad Wẽnd yaa Yaafd n yaa yolsg Naaba""."
  49,15,"Ad yaa muumin-rãmbã la neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Wẽnd la A Tẽn-tʋʋmã, rẽ poorẽ tɩ b pa maan sik ye, la b nidgd pãng ne b arzεgs la b mens Wẽnd sorã zugã; bãmb rãmbã la sɩd kõtba."
  49,16,"Yeele: ""yãmb wilgda Wẽnd y dĩini, tɩ Wẽnd yaool n mi bũmb ning sẽn be saasẽ la bũmb ning sẽn be tẽng zugu. Wẽnd yaa mit ne bũmbã fãa gilli""."
  49,17,"B tãasda foom tɩ b sak n tũ yĩnga. Yeele: ""ra tãas-y maam tɩ y sak-n-tũ yĩng ye. Wẽnd n sõmb n tãas yãmb ne A sẽn kãndg yãmb ne liimaoongã, tɩ yãmb sã n yaa sɩd-rãmba""."
  49,18,"Ad Wẽnd mii saasẽ yel-soondɩ la tẽng zug yel-soondɩ. Wẽnd yaa mit ne bũmb ning yãmb sẽn tʋmdã."
